{"$content":[{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_00_000","SpeakerName":"Nikola","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3202c4","IconName":"h3202c4_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Stop hiding. I know you've been following me for a while now.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_01_000","SpeakerName":"Nikola","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3202c4","IconName":"h3202c4_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"You thought that I was the type of kindhearted old man who'd adopt an orphan beggar from the streets out of pity?","sfxName":"human_male_middle_royal_08","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_01_001","SpeakerName":"Nikola","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3202c4","IconName":"h3202c4_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"If that's your purpose for following me, I advise you give up.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_01_002","SpeakerName":"Child","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3201c2","IconName":"h3201c2_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"......","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_02_000","SpeakerName":"Child","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3201c2","IconName":"h3201c2_sp1","IconLocate":2,"Text":"... Ugghh!","sfxName":"human_male_kid_10","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_03_000","SpeakerName":"Nikola","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3202c4","IconName":"h3202c4_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"You couldn't fool me by playing pity, so now you fake an illness? Hmph, that's why I said that brats these days... Hmm?","sfxName":"human_male_middle_royal_03","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_03_001","SpeakerName":"Nikola","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3202c4","IconName":"h3202c4_embarrass","IconLocate":2,"Text":"... This... Are you...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_04_000","SpeakerName":"Hyde","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0134","IconName":"h0134s3_sp1","IconLocate":2,"Text":"... Didn't expect the symptoms to surface now... Ugh,...","sfxName":"h0134_battle_hit_01_1_normal","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_04_001","SpeakerName":"Errand Soldier","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0055c2","IconName":"h0055c2_sp1","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Hey, are you alright?","sfxName":"human_male_young_08_ver1","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_05_000","SpeakerName":"Hyde","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0134","IconName":"h0134s3_embarrass","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Kingdom of the Sun soldier?","sfxName":"h0134_story_016_ver1","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_05_001","SpeakerName":"Hyde","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0134","IconName":"h0134s3_embarrass","IconLocate":2,"Text":"I'm fine, but we should leave this area as soon as possible...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_06_000","SpeakerName":"Messenger Soldier","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0057c3","IconName":"h0057c3_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"It's the beasts who inhabit this area!","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_06_001","SpeakerName":"Hyde","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0134","IconName":"h0134s3_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Let me help!","sfxName":"h0134_battle_attack_02_1_normal","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_07_000","SpeakerName":"Messenger Soldier","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0057c3","IconName":"h0057c3_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Thank you. You really helped us back there.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_07_001","SpeakerName":"Hyde","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0134","IconName":"h0134s3_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"It's me who has to thank you guys...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_07_002","SpeakerName":"Hyde","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0134","IconName":"h0134s3_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"By the way... this place is not exactly close to Kingdom of the Sun. Why are you two here? Do you have some kind of military mission?","sfxName":"h0134_story_002","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_07_003","SpeakerName":"Errand Soldier","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0055c2","IconName":"h0055c2_sp1","IconLocate":2,"Text":"To be honest, we're here on the orders of Regent Theodore. He wants us to visit the nearby village and locate a former minister name Nikola.","sfxName":"human_male_young_soldier_03","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_07_004","SpeakerName":"Errand Soldier","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0055c2","IconName":"h0055c2_sp1","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Have you ever heard of this person?","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_08_000","SpeakerName":"Hyde","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0134","IconName":"h0134s3_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Absolutely! I don't just know him; he's my teacher.","sfxName":"h0134_story_019_ver1","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_08_001","SpeakerName":"Messenger Soldier","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0057c3","IconName":"h0057c3_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"That's great to hear! Can you please introduce us to him?","sfxName":"human_male_young_13","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_08_002","SpeakerName":"Hyde","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0134","IconName":"h0134s3_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"You two helped me out. Of course I will take you to see Master. Only one problem... please remember to protect yourself when you meet him.","sfxName":"h0134_story_025","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_09_000","SpeakerName":"Nikola","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3202c4","IconName":"h3202c4_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"**** OFF !!","sfxName":"human_male_middle_royal_13","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_10_000","SpeakerName":"Nikola","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3202c4","IconName":"h3202c4_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Tell that Regent brat;
stop trying to interfere with my retirement life!","sfxName":"human_male_middle_royal_08","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_10_001","SpeakerName":"Messenger Soldier","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0057c3","IconName":"h0057c3_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"But... in order to prepare for the kingdom's 200th anniversary next year, Regent Theodore is already working around the clock.
He doesn't have the strength or time to handle other issues now.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_10_002","SpeakerName":"Messenger Soldier","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0057c3","IconName":"h0057c3_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"That's why he wanted to ask Minister Nikola to...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_10_003","SpeakerName":"Nikola","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3202c4","IconName":"h3202c4_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"You still talking? I said **** off!","sfxName":"human_male_middle_royal_12","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_11_000","SpeakerName":"Hyde","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0134","IconName":"h0134s3_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Calling Regent Theodore a brat... 
In the entire Kingdom of the Sun, I bet Master is the only one who's got the guts to say that.","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_11_001","SpeakerName":"Nikola","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3202c4","IconName":"h3202c4_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":"You don't get to laugh! You know my attitude very well. Why did you still bring the kingdom soldiers here?","sfxName":"human_male_middle_09","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_11_002","SpeakerName":"Hyde","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0134","IconName":"h0134s3_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"I can't really turn down their request. After all, those two soldiers did help me when my symptoms surfaced...","sfxName":"h0134_story_017","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_11_003","SpeakerName":"Nikola","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3202c4","IconName":"h3202c4_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"... Is it the void disease?","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_11_004","SpeakerName":"Hyde","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0134","IconName":"h0134s3_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Yes. The intervals between the symptom triggers seem to become more and more unstable...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_12_000","SpeakerName":"Nikola","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3202c4","IconName":"h3202c4_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"If that's all you're here for, go back to the school. The homework of those kids is still unmarked!","sfxName":"human_male_middle_royal_03","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_12_001","SpeakerName":"Hyde","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0134","IconName":"h0134s3_serious","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Understood, Master Nikola.","sfxName":"h0134_story_025","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_12_002","SpeakerName":"Hyde","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0134","IconName":"h0134s3_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Ah, right, Master. The place where my symptoms surfaced is exactly where we first met each other!","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_12_003","SpeakerName":"Nikola","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3202c4","IconName":"h3202c4_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Stop talking about the past! That was long ago!","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_12_004","SpeakerName":"Hyde","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0134","IconName":"h0134s3_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Master even said back then...","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_12_005","SpeakerName":"Hyde","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0134","IconName":"h0134s3_anger","IconLocate":2,"Text":""I'm not a kindhearted old man who'd adopt an orphan beggar from the streets simply out of pity!"","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_12_006","SpeakerName":"Hyde","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0134","IconName":"h0134s3_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Yet in the end, you took me home anyway and you raised me to where I am now~","sfxName":"h0134_story_025","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_12_007","SpeakerName":"Nikola","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3202c4","IconName":"h3202c4_embarrass","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Don't mention me in such a positive light. You're the one who refused to leave!","sfxName":"human_male_middle_royal_03","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0134_001_dialog_english##_12_008","SpeakerName":"Nikola","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h3202c4","IconName":"h3202c4_normal","IconLocate":2,"Text":"You little rascal; if I knew this was going to happen, I wouldn't have taken you in as my disciple in the first place!","sfxName":"","sfxVolume":1.0}]}
